div
    p User Name
    input(type='text', ng-model='newUser.user', placeholder='User Name', ng-change='validateUser()')
    p(ng-show='alerts.user') That user is already in use

    p E-Mail
    input(type='text', ng-model='newUser.email', placeholder='E-mail', ng-change='validateEmail()')
    p(ng-show='alerts.email') That email is already in use

    p Password
    input(type='password', ng-model='newUser.password', placeholder='password')

    button.submit__button(ng-click='createUser()', ng-show='newUser.password && newUser.user && newUser.email && !alerts.email && !alerts.user') Create User